      "id": "PopularPost159770",
      "post_content": "[Animate Artifact](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Animate Artifact) this son of a gun, then [Life And Limb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Life And Limb), so it is a land. Then, enchant it with [Wild Growth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wild Growth) or [Fertile Ground](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fertile Ground), and infinite away! Trust me, this is the easiest way to do an infinite mana combo with this!",
      "posted_by": "Superllama12",
