    {
      "id": "PopularPost154366",
      "post_content": "A classic example of a card that Wizards overlooked, and as a result, there are some pretty scary combos! If you have anything that prevents mana burn (the only one I can think ok at the moment is the  [Sakura Tribe Shaman](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Sakura Tribe Shaman ) , I'm such a n00b) then this thing can bring some pain! Just get this down ASAP (  [Dark Ritual](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Dark Ritual) anybody?) And then the shames, then, making sure that you're playing an artifact deck, lay as many artifacts as you can! It doesn't win you the game, but there are some combos with it that can!",
      "posted_by": "ninjaman98",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost154366\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">A classic example of a card that Wizards overlooked, and as a result, there are some pretty scary combos! If you have anything that prevents mana burn (the only one I can think ok at the moment is the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\" Sakura Tribe Shaman \" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Sakura Tribe Shaman \"> Sakura Tribe Shaman </a>, I'm such a n00b) then this thing can bring some pain! Just get this down ASAP ( <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\" Dark Ritual\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Dark Ritual\"> Dark Ritual</a> anybody?) And then the shames, then, making sure that you're playing an artifact deck, lay as many artifacts as you can! It doesn't win you the game, but there are some combos with it that can!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '154366'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy56524\">ninjaman98</span>\r\n                                (4/26/2011 1:02:40 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl0