    {
      "id": "PopularPost174277",
      "post_content": "@Long\\_Con  \n  \nFirst off, Reverse damage will never net you infinite life, as every trigger from [Artifact Possession](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Artifact Possession) is treated as a different source. That's probably what the Judge was talking about, with the ''combo not working''.  \n  \nSecondly, there's no ruling written that states you cannot use its mana to untap itself. the only combo that doesn't work is SuperLlama12's because he didn't include something to change its creature type to Saproling.  \n  \nWake Thrasher's most definitely the most original Idea I've seen to go with it, it was a little obscure since the Fae generally dominated Standard in that time.",
      "posted_by": "Snafinturtle",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost174277\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">@Long_Con<br/><br/>First off, Reverse damage will never net you infinite life, as every trigger from <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Artifact Possession\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Artifact Possession\">Artifact Possession</a> is treated as a different source. That's probably what the Judge was talking about, with the ''combo not working''.<br/><br/>Secondly, there's no ruling written that states you cannot use its mana to untap itself. the only combo that doesn't work is SuperLlama12's because he didn't include something to change its creature type to Saproling.<br/><br/>Wake Thrasher's most definitely the most original Idea I've seen to go with it, it was a little obscure since the Fae generally dominated Standard in that time.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '174277'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy49813\">Snafinturtle</span>\r\n                                (7/3/2011 2:45:23 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\